scenes.description: The members of hololive English -Justice- are excited and cheering as Gigi prepares for her turn.
Smokey explains the rules of the game on screen.
The group encourages Gigi and counts down to the start of the level.
Gigi plays Level 1 of 'Speed Block: Tick-Tock Takedown!'.
Gigi plays Level 3, which includes a posing challenge.
Gigi plays Level 4, which includes a tongue twister challenge.
Gigi plays Level 5, which includes a math challenge.
Gigi fails the math challenge, the bomb explodes, and the others react to her 'burnt' state.
Smokey gives points, and Raora prepares for her turn.
